# Environment Configuration

复制本文件为 `.env.local` 并填入真实的 API 密钥。

## DeepSeek LLM
```
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com
DEEPSEEK_CHAT_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro
```

## Jina Embeddings
```
JINA_API_KEY=jina_your-key-here
JINA_URL=https://api.jina.ai/v1/embeddings
JINA_MODEL=jina-embeddings-v3
```

## Qdrant Vector Database
```
QDRANT_URL=https://your-cluster.gcp.cloud.qdrant.io
QDRANT_API_KEY=your-jwt-token-here
QDRANT_COLLECTION=renti_listings_v2_jina
```

## Neo4j Graph Database
```
NEO4J_URI=neo4j+s://your-instance.databases.neo4j.io
NEO4J_USERNAME=your-username
NEO4J_PASSWORD=your-password
NEO4J_DATABASE=neo4j
```

## 高德地图（可选）
```
AMAP_WEB_KEY=your-amap-web-key
AMAP_WEB_SERVICE_KEY=your-amap-server-key
```

## 其他
```
PROXY_URL=http://127.0.0.1:7897
INTERNAL_TOKEN=your-secure-random-token
```
